🌹Jovie Rose Canela🌹born on Feb 10, 2023  at 14:56 pm. A completely unmedicated vaginal birth 💫 words cannot describe this feeling. We fell in love with her the moment we knew she was inside me and although this sounds cliche, our love has only multiplied with every single second that passes since 14:56pm on that day. To all the super mommas out there, I just want to say, WE GOT THIS ! @jasoncanela and I are looking forward to it all as we promise to be there every step of the way for our precious baby girl ❤️ thank you to all of our friends and family that have been praying for us and sending such positive vibes throughout these last 9 months.

I Can’t believe our baby is already one month ! 

We always knew what a blessing it was to be welcoming you to our world and anxiously waited out those 9 months wondering what you looked like, what you smelled like, what you would be like but never in a million years could we have imagined that you would be so unimaginably perfect in our eyes. Today marks 1 month since you were born, you are latched on to mama pretty much every other hour and in between feeds papa is changing your diapers and making sure you’re as comfortable as can be. Your family extends all around the globe, from the Brazilian side to the Cuban side you will only always know the purest of loves ❤️✨ happy 1 month Jovie 🌹
